(June 15, 1950.)

(Republish.)

Katherine W. Carr, Respondent, v. Francis J. Carr, Appellant.

Order, so far as appealed from, modified in accordance with the Per Curiam opinion herein. Present — Peck, P. J., Dore, Cohn, Callahan and Yan Yoorhis, JJ.; Dore, J., dissents in part in opinion. Settle order on one day’s notice. [See ante, p. 861; post, p. 865.]
